{"type": "article", "id": 2529, "title": "防止打翻水杯的Mighty Mug", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-24T08:23:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232553k1s8YKV625GDwILA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t不小心打翻桌上的水杯这件事，不少人都干过，除了怪自己毛手毛脚之外，只能警告自己下次别再干这种蠢事。设计师 Jayme Smaldone 为此专门花费 3 年时间开发出一项名为“ Smartgrip ”的专利技术，推出了一款特别的产品“ Mighty Mug ”，只需在杯子底部安装一个抓地力极强的气阀，使其稳稳地站在桌面上，避免出现贸然被打翻的窘况。需要喝水时，则可以正常端起。Jayme Smaldone  为 Mighty Mug 设计了不同造型、不同容量的选择，目前正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/jayme39/mighty-mug-the-mug-that-wont-fall\" target=\"_blank\">Kickstarter </a>上进行众筹。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/002/486/406/3c6fb6f2eec7ca458cd8615da86861b6_large.gif?1408999863\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/002/485/405/3646bff42434c240c857a8d591dbad3e_large.gif?1408988250\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232551WKecoYqdsADx4j2N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232552YsTvhkKeNA5OQWa0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232552nH2KbsABNTkdigV9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\n\n"}